Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:17.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次點燃時代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,yeah boom 著火 no matter what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:22.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,照天燒 burn the fire just set on the 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,荒唐無稽的上進心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,空中漂浮 現在Time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一心不亂加堅忍不拔 alright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不是孤身一人 let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不要停下 來創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:45.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,如夜裡的花一般 無人欣賞也綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:51.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,從過去繼承的flame 在胸口沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:52.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,We'are going higher 強烈的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:03:02.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次點燃時代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:06.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,將粉碎的命運收回手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,緊密連結的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:15.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,化為無形的光
